{"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"@discardableResult"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"onNotifyDomain","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"flags","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject12ConnectFlagsV","text":"ConnectFlags","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" = ConnectFlags(0), ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"handler"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"keyword","text":"@escaping"},{"text":" (","kind":"text"},{"text":"MountOperationRef","preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO17MountOperationRefV","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/MountOperationRef","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject12ParamSpecRefV","text":"ParamSpecRef","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":") -> "},{"text":"Void","preciseIdentifier":"s:s4Voida","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Int","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si"}],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"parameters":[{"name":"flags","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Flags"}]}]},{"name":"handler","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The signal handler to call"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"Run the given callback whenever the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"notifyDomain"},{"type":"text","text":" signal is emitted"}]}]}],"kind":"parameters"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Discussion","level":2,"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Note that getting this signal doesn’t itself guarantee that the value of"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the property has actually changed. When it is emitted is determined by the","type":"text"},{"type":"text